description:
UEFA.Champions.League.Extra.Time.2013.12.10.HDTV.x264-W4F

Highlights of this evening's matchday six fixtures, which included    
Manchester United v Shakhtar Donetsk at Old Trafford, Galatasaray v   
Juventus at the Turk Telekom Arena and Bayern Munich v Manchester     
City at the Allianz Arena. Several issues were still to be decided,   
with places in the last 16 and the consolation of dropping into the   
UEFA Europa League up for grabs. Presented by Matt Smith, with        
commentary by Clive Tyldesley and Andy Townsend.
